OL,3,CRiver Dart among new bathing spots
OL,4,Cbeing proposed across country
OL,6,FStretches of river and parts of the
OL,7,Fcoast across the South West will
OL,8,Fbecome designated swimming spots as
OL,9,Fpart of Government plans to establish
OL,10,Fdozens of new bathing water sites.
OL,12,FIf designated, the sites would receive
OL,13,Fregular water monitoring by the
OL,14,FEnvironment Agency, to investigate
OL,15,Fpollution sources and identify steps
OL,16,Fto be taken in response, officials
OL,17,Fsaid.
