OL,6,FThis means swimmers would be able to
OL,7,Fsee whether it was safe to enter the
OL,8,Fwaters, which include popular "wild
OL,9,Fswimming" spots.
OL,11,FSeven out of the 27 new proposed areas
OL,12,Fare in the South West:
OL,14,FThe Environment Department (Defra)
OL,15,Fsaid last year 96% of bathing waters
OL,16,Fin England met minimum annual
OL,17,Fstandards and 90% were rated as "good"
OL,18,For "excellent".
