OL,3,CRiver Dart among new bathing spots
OL,4,Cbeing proposed across country
OL,6,FBut there has been growing public
OL,7,Fanger over the state of England's
OL,8,Frivers and coastal waters, which
OL,9,Fsuffer pollution from sewage outlets
OL,10,Fand other sources such as agricultural
OL,11,Frunoff.
OL,13,FThere were 424 designated bathing
OL,14,Fwaters in England in 2023, with only a
OL,15,Fhandful of them inland, and the vast
OL,16,Fmajority on the coast.
OL,18,FThis announcement has been described
OL,19,Fas the largest ever rollout of new
OL,20,Fbathing sites.
