OL,6,FWater minister, Robbie Moore said:
OL,7,F"Many people enjoy spending time in
OL,8,Four rivers, lakes and coastal beaches,
OL,9,Fand I am very aware of the value they
OL,10,Fbring in terms of social, health and
OL,11,Fwellbeing benefits.
OL,13,F"I want to continue to improve the
OL,14,Fquality of our bathing waters, which
OL,15,Fis why we are taking action across the
OL,16,Fboard to drive up standards and hold
OL,17,Fwater companies to account.
