OL,6,F"I encourage all local communities and
OL,7,Forganisations with an interest to take
OL,8,Fpart in this consultation and have
OL,9,Ftheir say."
OL,11,FBut, Liberal Democrat environment
OL,12,Fspokesperson Tim Farron said:
OL,13,F"Conservative ministers have finally
OL,14,Fbuckled to Liberal Democrat demands
OL,15,Ffor more bathing water sites, but the
OL,16,Fgrim truth is water firms have dumped
OL,17,Fover 400,000 hours of sewage into
OL,18,Fswimming spots since 2020.
