OL,6,F"The government has yet again been
OL,7,Fdragged kicking and screaming to take
OL,8,Faction on water quality.
OL,10,FThe sites put forward for
OL,11,Fconsultation, which runs until March
OL,12,F10, were chosen based on how many
OL,13,Fpeople bathe there and whether it has
OL,14,Fsuitable facilities such as toilets.
