OL,3,CRiver Dart among new bathing spots
OL,4,Cbeing proposed across country
OL,6,FDefra said the consultation on the new
OL,7,Fdesignations would build on recent
OL,8,Fimprovements to the water environment,
OL,9,Fwhich includes boosting the number of
OL,10,Fwater company inspections by the
OL,11,FEnvironment Agency, and requiring a
OL,12,F#60 billion infrastructure programme
OL,13,Fover 25 years.
OL,15,FChairman of the parliamentary
OL,16,FEnvironmental Audit Committee, Tory MP
OL,17,FPhilip Dunne, said the designation of
OL,18,Finland waters would boost monitoring
OL,19,Fand encourage efforts to tackle poor
OL,20,Fwater quality.
