OL,6,FHe said: "This huge uptick in
OL,7,Fdesignation of sites in England which
OL,8,Fwill be required to have bathing-
OL,9,Fquality waters shows a determination
OL,10,Fto deliver consistently high levels of
OL,11,Fwater quality in areas the public
OL,12,Fdemand it."
